text: João Pedro Furtado da Cunha Semedo (20 June 1951 - 17 July 2018), was a Portuguese physician and politician. He was a member of Assembly of the Republic from March 2006 to March 2015. He was born in Lisbon. Semedo died on 17 July 2018 in Lisbon at the age of 67.Morreu João Semedo (1951-2018) ==References== Category:1951 births Category:2018 deaths Category:Physicians Category:Politicians from Lisbon
